<section class="content" role="main">
  <div class="container"> 
    <!-- Culture -->
    <div class="row-fluid" id="culture">
      <h4 style="padding-top: 0px; background-image: url(http://www.noah-consulting.com/assets/img/2.gif); background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 60%; background-repeat: repeat-x;"><span class="sm-gray">Our</span><span class="bold-dk-blue">Culture</span></h4>
      <p>We work tirelessly to maintain a culture where people want to work.  Our foundation is built on integrity, honesty, professionalism, and work-life balance, which creates a culture that starts at the top and lives in all of our employees, the Noah family. Members of the Noah family are experts in consulting, technology, and the energy industry. We only hire the best. Many are veterans with decades of experience in the energy business and first-hand knowledge of specific industry-related problems and information management solutions. Noah Consulting is a home for focused experts with a common passion.</p>
      <p>Some of the things that make Noah a great place to work include:</p>
      <ul class="two-col">
        <li><strong>Noah Happenings:</strong> our culture committee</li>
        <li><strong>Mentor Program:</strong> advocacy, guidance, support, and oversight in career planning</li>
        <li><strong>Buddy Program:</strong> a jump-start on internal networking and smoother on-boarding</li>
        <li><strong>Career Ladder:</strong> transparency in the steps required to advance from one level to the next</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <!-- Awards -->
    <div class="row-fluid" id="awards">
      <h4><span class="gray">Award</span><span class="bold-lt-blue">Winning</span><span class="dk-blue">Culture</span></h4>
