  <ul class="opps-list">
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?i1=PUBLIC&i2=726996648113805&i3=DETAIL&i4=726996648113805&i5=&i6=&i7=&i8=6%2F5%2F2015%2012:46:17%20PM&hash=63190900&i10=&pcr-id=0SEqBkM0GnTikuG2hPvbCWlF0wJnsb%2FLm0Tt15weUM6PWNp4qw2CMHuFD7lKV61eKl10MQpNrAWWtNy4ryLfU%2BFvNg1uBBwg%2F0K3vaDoDF335bKrnA%3D%3D"> <strong>Business Analyst</strong> <span>The business analyst identifies and develops the conceptual solution and business requirements for the information management program or project. </span></a> </li>
    
    
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?i1=PUBLIC&i2=590334737615988&i3=DETAIL&i4=590334737615988&i5=&i6=&i7=&i8=6%2F5%2F2015%2012:46:17%20PM&hash=311280628&i10=&pcr-id=0SEqBkM0GnTikuG2hPvbCWlF0wJnsb%2FLm0Tt15weUM6PWNp4qw2CMHuFD7lKV61eKl10MQpNrAWWtNy4ryLfU%2BFvNg1uBBwg%2F0K3vaDoDF335bKrnA%3D%3D"> <strong>Data Architect</strong> <span>Data architects interact with senior business and IT clients to provide team leadership and hands-on technical and functional expertise.</span></a> </li>
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?i1=PUBLIC&i2=149024753205617&i3=DETAIL&i4=149024753205617&i5=&i6=&i7=&i8=6%2F5%2F2015%2012:46:17%20PM&hash=409487801&i10=&pcr-id=0SEqBkM0GnTikuG2hPvbCWlF0wJnsb%2FLm0Tt15weUM6PWNp4qw2CMHuFD7lKV61eKl10MQpNrAWWtNy4ryLfU%2BFvNg1uBBwg%2F0K3vaDoDF335bKrnA%3D%3D"> <strong>Data Modeler / Analyst</strong> <span>A data modeler/analyst must have expertise in relational and dimensional data modeling and enterprise data management methodologies as well as possess the ability to analyze large volumes of data for business rules definition and validation. </span></a> </li>
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?db=z3uOeNUcREYKKL9yfgE7M1Mlqfjrp8XHDX4FJabC&jobid=176027993782537&src=%5b%5bsrc%5d%5d"> <strong>Enterprise Architect</strong> <span>Seeking an Enterprise Architect who understand the business side of EA, namely Business Architecture and Information Architecture.</span></a> </li>
    
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?i1=PUBLIC&i2=471493456393026&i3=DETAIL&i4=471493456393026&i5=&i6=&i7=&i8=6%2F5%2F2015%2012:46:17%20PM&hash=219421584&i10=&pcr-id=0SEqBkM0GnTikuG2hPvbCWlF0wJnsb%2FLm0Tt15weUM6PWNp4qw2CMHuFD7lKV61eKl10MQpNrAWWtNy4ryLfU%2BFvNg1uBBwg%2F0K3vaDoDF335bKrnA%3D%3D"> <strong>Project Manager</strong> <span>The project manager directs project execution from beginning to end to ensure successful implementation as defined in the statement of work. </span></a> </li>
    <li><a href="http://www2.pcrecruiter.net/pcrbin/reg5.aspx?i1=PUBLIC&i2=395558082877375&i3=DETAIL&i4=395558082877375&i5=&i6=&i7=&i8=6%2F5%2F2015%2012:46:17%20PM&hash=1403231091&i10=&pcr-id=0SEqBkM0GnTikuG2hPvbCWlF0wJnsb%2FLm0Tt15weUM6PWNp4qw2CMHuFD7lKV61eKl10MQpNrAWWtNy4ryLfU%2BFvNg1uBBwg%2F0K3vaDoDF335bKrnA%3D%3D"> <strong>Subject Matter Expert</strong> <span>A subject matter expert must have industry-specific experience and the ability relate the technical and business aspects of data. </span></a> </li>
